fields.name: God of War Ragnarok
fields.description: God of War: Ragnarok is an action-adventure computer game with hack and slash elements, developed by Santa Monica Studio and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment.

fields.name: Marvel's Spider-Man
fields.description: Marvel's Spider-Man 2 is an action-adventure video game developed by Insomniac Games in collaboration with Marvel Games and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment.

fields.name: Minecraft
fields.description: Minecraft is an indie sandbox computer game created by Swedish programmer Markus Persson and published by his studio Mojang AB.

fields.name: The Last Of Us Part II
fields.description: The Last of Us Part II is an action-adventure computer game with elements of survival horror and third-person stealth action, developed by Naughty Dog and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment in 2020 for the PlayStation 4 game console.
